c: 11
v: 87
t: "Thus still they said to him: \"Do your prayers, O Shuaib, and system of faith enjoin you to induce us to renounce Our father's system of faith and worship or that we must not use our money at will nor do with it what we will!\". But we have always thought you were AL-Halim (the forbearing) and AL-Rashid (a man of min)"